# Local dev for the Ask-the-research chat (functions/api/ask.ts).
# Copy to .dev.vars for `wrangler pages dev`, or export before `pnpm cf:dev`.
# In production these live in the Cloudflare Pages project (encrypted).

# Required for the chat to work (otherwise it degrades gracefully):
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# Optional: override the chat model (defaults to claude-opus-4-8).
# CHAT_MODEL=claude-opus-4-8
